br/>But that=E2=80=99s not to say either opening qualifies as a disappointm=
ent. <b>Jon M. Chu</b>=E2=80=99s $145 million fantasy starring <b>Ariana Gr=
ande</b> and <b>Cynthia Erivo</b> debuted to $112.5 million in North Americ=
